			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Nisim nisimin biakinn sungah thuhilhin note tawh ka omkhawm a, ahi zongin nong man kei uh hi. Ahi zongin hih thu pen Lai Siangtho sunga a kigelh thu a tun nading ahi hi,” a ci hi.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Tua ciangin a nungzuite khempeuh in Jesuh a taisan uh hi.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Puanza kang khat bek a silh tangval khat in zong Jesuh a zui hi. Amaute pawlkhat in amah a mat ciangin,",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> a puanza kang nusia-in a guaktangin a tai hi.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Mihonte in siampi lianpen pa’ inn-ah Jesuh paipih uh a, siampi liante, upate, le Thukham hilh siate hong kikhawm uh hi.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Peter in zong Jesuh’ nung galzuih a, siampi lianpen pa’ inntual ciangah a om hi. Tua lai-ah palikte tawh mei awi-in a tukhawm hi.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Siampi liante a kipan uliante khempeuh in Jesuh a thahtheih nadingin thu zong uh a, ahi zongin bangmah mu lo uh hi.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Mi tampi in amah a mawhsak nadingun zuauthu gen uh a, ahi zongin a genna uh khatlekhat kituak lo hi.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Tua ciangin mi pawlkhat hong dingin amah a mawhsak nadingun zuauthu hong gen uh a,",
