			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Amaute nangawn zong a thugenzia uh kituak lo hi.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Tua ciangin amaute khempeuh mai-ah siampi lianpen pa hong dingin Jesuh thu dong a, “Nangmah mawhsakna-in a gen uh thute na dawn nading om lo ahi hiam?” ci-in a dong hi.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Ahi zongin Jesuh pau loin a omcip hi. Tua ciangin siampi lianpen pa in, “Phatna a ngah Pasian’ Tapa, Khrih na hi hiam?” ci-in a dongkik leuleu hi.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Jesuh in, “Ka hi hi; Vanglian Pasian’ taklamah Mihing Tapa omin meii lakah a hong pai na mu ding uh hi,” a ci hi.",
