			"64": "<sup>64</sup> Pasian’ tungah a paukhialhna na zazo uh hi. Bangci ngaihsut na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. Hih mipa thah dingin kilawm hi, ci-in amaute khempeuh in thu a khen uh hi.",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> Tua ciangin mi pawlkhat in cilphih uh a, a mai tunsakin beeng uh a, “Kua in hong beng ahi hiam, gen in,” a ci uh hi. Palikte in zong amah paipihin a beeng uh hi.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> A nuai-a inntualah Peter a om laitakin siampi lianpen pa’ nasem numeite khat hong pai a,",
