			"69": "<sup>69</sup> Tua numei mah in a omna-ah Peter mu a, a gei-a omte kiangah, “Hih pa, hua mite khat hi takpi hi,” a cikik leuleu hi.",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> Ahi zongin Peter in nial leuleu hi. Tawlkhat khit ciangin a gei-a omte in Peter kiangah, “Nang zong Galilee gammi na hih manin huate khat na hi takpi hi,” a ci leuleu uh hi.",
