			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Tua bangin a pai laitakun, Alexander le Rufas’ pa, Sairin khuami Simon a kici mi khat, gam sung panin khuapi sunga hong pai tawh kituak uh a, Jesuh’ singlamteh a pua dingin lammat uh hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Lutang guh a cihnopna Golgotha  munah paipih uh a,",
